Website Owners

Monetize your website traffic by featuring SkyCart products and deals.

Email Marketers

Promote SkyCart products to your email subscribers and earn commissions.

Digital Marketers

Know Your Audience

Frequently Asked Questions

How much can I earn?

Earnings vary based on your traffic, audience, and promotional strategy. Our top affiliates earn hundreds of thousands of rupees per month.

Is there a cost to join?

No, joining our affiliate program is completely free. There are no setup fees or monthly charges.

Can I promote SkyCart on social media?

Yes! You can share your affiliate links on all major social media platforms, following their terms of service.

How do I track my earnings?

Our affiliate dashboard provides real-time tracking of clicks, conversions, and earnings. You can access it 24/7.

What products can I promote?

You can promote any product available on SkyCart, including physical products, digital downloads, and services.
